Fifteen persons have lost their lives in a boat mishap at Dandeji village in the Shagari Local Government Area of Sokoto State. The accident reportedly occurred on Wednesday. According to Aliyu Abubakar, a political administrator of the LGA, more than 15 children drowned, and 25 others are missing. Abubakar said, ‘’Fifteen bodies, 13 girls and two boys were recovered by local rescue teams and buried in the village.